  "descriptions": {
    "en": {
      "language": "en",
      "value": "court noble in the middle of the Edo period. Seven generations of the Tsutsumi family. Second rank, Chunagon. The second son of Toshikiyo Bojo. Mother is also the housewife"
    },
    "ja": {
      "language": "ja",
      "value": "江戸時代中期の公卿。堤家7代。正二位、中納言。坊城俊清の次男。母はあるいは家女房"
    }
